name: Knitted Bow Headband, Knitted Headband, Cute and Cosy Ear Warmer in Sparkly Glitter Christmas Red
description:
♥ This knitted bow headband, knitted headband, sparkly glitter knitted headband in Christmas festive red is a cute and cosy style ear warmer autumn winter hair accessory, and essential to see you through the chilly months! With this super sweet knitted bow headband you can still look stylish with this completely adorable stretchy headband with bow! 
♥ This headband has been knitted with a lovely, cosy, soft sparkly glitter baby wool and the shimmer is so sweet and makes this knitted headband so unique. Because of the way it is made, you can pull the bow out as much as you like to make the look work for you. Furthermore, you can either wear the bow to the side of your head or on top, either way, it's the most adorable option this winter! 
♥ My knitted headband, with a super cute big bow, is the perfect way to keep you warm this winter and can be worn over the ears to keep you warm. Super soft and snuggly. Super stretchy, so one size fits most adults and teens. Hand knitted by Beauxoxo.
